\v 5 If anyoneВҰ146508 of you is lackingВҰ146510 wisdomВҰ146511, then it shouldВҰ146512 be requestedВҰ146512 from \nd GodВҰ146518\nd* who gives it generouslyВҰ146520 and without disparagement, and so it will be givenВҰ146526 to you,
\v 6 butВҰ146529 the person who's asking shouldВҰ146528 demonstrate their faithВҰ146531 and not be doubting. That's becauseВҰ146535 a person who doubts is like a wave on the seaВҰ146539 that's just blownВҰ146540 and tossedВҰ146542 around
