\v 23 Anyone who is just a listenerВҰ146797 of the messageВҰ146798 andВҰ146800 does nothing with it is like someone who looks at their faceВҰ146809 in a mirrorВҰ146814
\v 24 butВҰ146818 goes away after having a look and then immediatelyВҰ146821 forgets what they looked like.
\v 25 However the person who investigatesВҰ146827 the perfectВҰ146830 law that gives freedomВҰ146833, and then sticks with it, not being just an observer that forgetsВҰ146839 about it butВҰ146826 rather a person who puts it into practice, this person will prosper in whatever they do.
