\v 27 A person who wants to truly serve ourВҰ146881 \nd GodВҰ146882\nd* and fatherВҰ146885 with a pure heart would be visitingВҰ146888 orphansВҰ146889 and widowsВҰ146891 in theirВҰ146895 difficulties and staying unstained by worldlyВҰ146903 ideas.
