\p
\v 1 MyВҰ146905 dear brothersВҰ146904 andВҰ146904 sistersВҰ146904, as you live out your faithВҰ146911 in ourВҰ146914 honoured \nd masterВҰ146913 YeshuaВҰ146915\nd* the \nd messiahВҰ146916\nd*, don'tВҰ146906 show favouritismВҰ146908 to others.
