\v 7 SoВҰ148158 my fellowВҰ148159 believersВҰ148159, be patient until the return of \add Yeshua our\add* \nd masterВҰ148164\nd*. You see how farmersВҰ148167 lookВҰ148165 forward to the fruitВҰ148171 to be readyвҖ”waiting patiently even while they monitor the earlyВҰ148184 andВҰ148185 the late rainsВҰ148186.
