\p
\v 9 And don'tВҰ148209 moan about each other, my fellowВҰ148203 believersВҰ148203, so that youВҰ148210 all won'tВҰ148209 be judgedВҰ148210 for it, because truly, the judgeВҰ148214 is just outside about to come in the doorsВҰ148217.
\v 10 Look at the prophetsВҰ148233 who spokeВҰ148235 out the messages from \nd YahwehВҰ148239\nd*вҖ”they're good examplesВҰ148219 of suffering andВҰ148228 patienceВҰ148230 \add for you to follow\add*
\v 11 and now we consider them as heroes for their endurance. You all heardВҰ148248 about Yob's endurance and then you yourselves witnessed what happened to \add Yeshua our\add* master,\x + \xo 5:11: a \xt Yob 1:21-22; 2:10; \xo b \xt Psa 103:8.\x* and you saw his compassion and mercy.
\p
\v 12 ButВҰ148288 most importantly, brothersВҰ148265 and sistersВҰ148265, don'tВҰ148267 swearВҰ148268 by heavenВҰ148271 or earthВҰ148274 or by any otherВҰ148276 kind of oath butВҰ148288 simply be honest so that вҖҳyesвҖҷ means yes and вҖҳnoвҖҷ means no,\x + \xo 5:12: \xt Mat 5:34-37.\x* then you won'tВҰ148267 end up getting judgedВҰ148296.
\s1 The power of prayer and restoration
\rem /s1 The Prayer of Faith
\rem /s1 The Power of Prayer
\p
\v 13 Is anyone amongВҰ148300 youВҰ148301 going through hard times? If so, they should be prayingВҰ148302. Is anyone feeling cheerfulВҰ148303? If so, they should be singingВҰ148307 praisesВҰ148307.
\v 14 Is anyoneВҰ148309 amongВҰ148311 youВҰ148312 sick? If so, that person shouldВҰ148313 call the leaders \add of the assemblyВҰ148317\add* and get them to anointВҰ148323 them with oilВҰ148325 and to pray for them\x + \xo 5:14: \xt Mrk 6:13.\x* in the nameВҰ148328 and authority of \add Yeshua\add* \add &our\add* \nd masterВҰ148330\nd*.
\v 15 ThenВҰ148331 that declaration of faithВҰ148335 will save the weak person and the \nd masterВҰ148343\nd* will lift him/her up, and if they've sinned, thenВҰ148331 their sinsВҰ148345 will also be forgivenВҰ148348.
\v 16 SoВҰ148351 confessВҰ148350 yourВҰ148353 sinsВҰ148355 to each other andВҰ148357 pray for each other so that all of youВҰ148363 can be healedВҰ148363, because when an obedient believer prays, it has a real effect.
\v 17 Eliyah was a person just similar to us, and when he prayedВҰ148375 for the rain to stop, it stopped, and it didn'tВҰ148378 rain again for threeВҰ148388 and a half yearsВҰ148386.\x + \xo 5:17: \xt 1Ki 17:1; 18:1.\x*
\v 18 ThenВҰ148392 he prayedВҰ148394 again, and the rain came down from the skyВҰ148397 and the land sproutedВҰ148405 and started to bear fruitВҰ148407 again.\x + \xo 5:18: \xt 1Ki 18:42-45.\x*
\rem /s1 Restore Wandering Believers
\p
\v 19 MyВҰ148410 fellowВҰ148409 believersВҰ148409, if any of youВҰ148414 have wandered from the truthВҰ148420 andВҰ148421 someoneВҰ148423 helps them back,
